""" Ensures the class attributes for SessionSummary are created."""
with patch(
    f'{DATAFRAMES_PATH}.generic.generic_models.AbstractGenericModel.get_data'
    ), patch(f'{ABSTRACT_GENERIC}.GenericMediator'), patch(
    f'{ABSTRACT_GENERIC}.Authenticator'):
    with self.subTest():
        summary = SessionSummary()
        with self.subTest():
            self.assertIsNotNone(summary.app)
        with self.subTest():
            self.assertIsNotNone(summary.device)
        with self.subTest():
            self.assertIsNotNone(summary.location)
        with self.subTest():
            self.assertIsNotNone(summary.metrics)
        with self.subTest():
            self.assertIsNotNone(summary.network_app_usage)
